OL,3,CFamily of Oxfordshire man who died
OL,4,Cfrom MND raise more than #50,000
OL,6,FITV Meridian reporter Natalie Verney
OL,7,Fhas been speaking to Mark's family and
OL,8,Ffriends
OL,10,FThe daughter and son of a man from
OL,11,FOxfordshire who died from Motor
OL,12,FNeurone Disease have raised more than
OL,13,F#50,000 for charity by cycling the
OL,14,Flength of the country in his honour.
OL,16,FThey are riding in memory of their
OL,17,Ffather, accountant Mark Smith, who
OL,18,Fdied last year after being diagnosed
OL,19,Fwith the condition which affects the
OL,20,Fbrain and nerves.
