OL,3,CFamily of Oxfordshire man who died
OL,4,Cfrom MND raise more than #50,000
OL,6,FThe money will go towards research in
OL,7,Fthe hope that one day a cure will be
OL,8,Ffound.
OL,10,FThe route - from Morpeth to Norfolk to
OL,11,FDorset - spelled out the disease that
OL,12,Ftook his life.
OL,14,FMark's family told ITV News: "I miss
OL,15,Fhim just being here really, just being
OL,16,Fpart of the family. He was a big, big
OL,17,Ffamily man. He loved an adventure.
OL,18,FWe'd ski with him, and go surfing and
OL,19,Fyeah he loved the outdoors doing
OL,20,Fthings with and for his family."
