OL,6,FWhen they get injured those messages
OL,7,Fdon't get through and paralysis takes
OL,8,Fover.
OL,10,FBefore Mark passed away, he wanted to
OL,11,Ffundraise for research to help find a
OL,12,Fcure.
OL,14,FIn his final months, Mark helped his
OL,15,Ffamily plan a challenge to cycle the
OL,16,Flength of England.
OL,18,FDay 10 of the challenge was
OL,19,Fparticularly special, when six of the
OL,20,Fmedics who'd treated Mark at the John
OL,21,FRadcliffe Hospital joined in.
