OL,6,FHe said: "I was really privileged to
OL,7,Fbe asked. And I think as a team, as
OL,8,Fthe MND team in Oxford we cycle
OL,9,Ftogether a lot for various challenges
OL,10,Fso once I mentioned it to everybody
OL,11,Fthey were really keen to be asked."
OL,12,FMark had expected them to raise #2000
OL,13,Fbut in the end the team raised more
OL,14,Fthan #50,000.
OL,16,FThe money will go to the MND
OL,17,FAssociation and the the Oxford Motor
OL,18,FNeurone Disease Centre.
